{
  "texts": [
    "These studies focused on using structured data as input variables instead of clinical text.",
    "More recently, CAML model exhibited superior ability to predict DRGs 13.",
    "CAML model, exclusively utilizing clinical notes, surpassed the performance of a Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) model using structured clinical variables 13.",
    "When compared with ClinicalBERT, CAML provided improved F1 scores but lower AUC 13, 15.",
    "We observed that DRG- Experiments were performed on LLaMA with a size of 7 billion and 13 billion parameters."
  ]
}